|--- Anguish Overlord Mata Muram

Sub Event_OMMGaze
		/declare i int
		/declare j int
		
			/for i 1 to 5
				/exchange "Mirrored Mask" face
				/stopcast
				/twist off
				/stick off
				/stand
				/delay 1
			/next i
		
		/delay 1s
		
			/for i 1 to 30
			:top
				/casting "Mirrored Mask"
				/if (${Cast.Status.NotEqual[I]}) /goto :top
				/delay 1
				/echo BOSSMODS: Attempting to Click Mirrored Mask!
			/next i
			
		/if (${Me.Class.Name.Equal[Bard]}) {
			/twist start
		}		
/return

